cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper deals with learning mechanisms in neural networks, specifically spiking neural networks. The focus is on adaptivity and forgetting of insignificant data while retaining significant information. This falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with recognition and denoising of input data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with real-time on-line learning in a dynamic environment, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY).
